{"type": "article", "id": 25975, "title": "可以收线的手机充电器", "description": "", "date": "2016-04-26T07:35:52Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 29, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702144027AIBvYfuZLOlNFc84.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">来自纽约的设计师 <a href=\"http://www.dezeen.com/tag/karim-rashid/\">Karim Rashid</a> 带来了这款名为 Bump 的手机充电器，在不使用的情况下可以和收纳充电线（长 1 米）的中空圆环拼在一起，便于随身携带。充电器上的指示灯代表了剩余电量，它的开关是位于下方的圆形按钮。小巧的体积和明亮的颜色都是让人爱不释手的理由。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702144025tHQlZnRKBwjkqEz9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702144025coJyWr0GFS5K2ZEB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702144026D6BLQf8hrk9q2wpH.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021440267hyK5e3ACmBbOEdZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}